name: Killer Queen - Live Game - Last Game

panels.name: Likelihood to Win
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$killerQueen gamestate
| parse "com.sumologic.killerqueen.state.StateMachine - *" as json_text | json field=json_text "event"
| json field=json_text "gameId"
| json field=json_text "lastKnownSnailPosition"
| json field=json_text "secondsSinceGameStart"
| int(secondsSinceGameStart) as secondsSinceGameStart
| long(gameid) as gameid
| json field=json_text "goldQueenLivesRemaining", "blueQueenLivesRemaining", "goldBerriesRemaining", "blueBerriesRemaining"
| int(goldQueenLivesRemaining) as goldQueenLivesRemaining
| int(blueQueenLivesRemaining) as blueQueenLivesRemaining
| int(goldBerriesRemaining) as goldBerriesRemaining
| int(blueBerriesRemaining) as blueBerriesRemaining
| int(lastKnownSnailPosition) as lastKnownSnailPosition
//Snail
| lastKnownSnailPosition - 960 as lastKnownSnailPosition
| -960 as blue_snail
| 960 as gold_snail
| if(lastKnownSnailPosition<0, 100*lastKnownSnailPosition/blue_snail, 0) as blueSnailWinPercent
| if(lastKnownSnailPosition>0, 100*lastKnownSnailPosition/gold_snail, 0) as goldSnailWinPercent
//Percentage completion
| 100*(3-goldQueenLivesRemaining)/3 as blueQueenWinPercent
| 100*(3-blueQueenLivesRemaining)/3 as goldQueenWinPercent
| 100*(12-goldBerriesRemaining)/12 as goldBerriesWinPercent
| 100*(12-blueBerriesRemaining)/12 as blueBerriesWinPercent

//Find the highest percentage for Blue 
| blueBerriesWinPercent as blueWinPercent
| if( blueWinPercent < blueQueenWinPercent, blueQueenWinPercent, blueWinPercent) as blueWinPercent
| if( blueWinPercent < blueSnailWinPercent, blueSnailWinPercent, blueWinPercent) as blueWinPercent

//Find the highest percentage for Gold 
| goldBerriesWinPercent as goldWinPercent
| if( goldWinPercent < goldQueenWinPercent, goldQueenWinPercent, goldWinPercent) as goldWinPercent
| if( goldWinPercent < goldSnailWinPercent, goldSnailWinPercent, goldWinPercent) as goldWinPercent

//Combine for one percentage
| 0 as winPercent
| if( goldWinPercent >= blueWinPercent, goldWinPercent , -blueWinPercent ) as winPercent

| max(winPercent) as winPercent, max(blueWinPercent) as blueWinPercent, max(goldWinPercent) as goldWinPercent by gameid, secondsSinceGameStart
| -blueWinPercent as blueWinPercent
| sort by secondsSinceGameStart asc
| filter gameid in (max(gameid) as gameid)
| fields secondsSinceGameStart, winPercent
| 100 as gold
| -100 as blue
| fields secondsSinceGameStart, gold, blue, winPercent

panels.name: Berries Remaining
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$killerQueen gamestate
| parse "com.sumologic.killerqueen.state.StateMachine - *" as json_text | json field=json_text "event"
| json field=json_text "gameId"
| json field=json_text "goldQueenLivesRemaining", "blueQueenLivesRemaining"
| json field=json_text "goldBerriesRemaining","blueBerriesRemaining"
| json field=json_text "blueBots", "blueNormalWorkers","blueSpeedWorkers", "blueNormalWarriors", "blueSpeedWarriors"
| json field=json_text "goldBots","goldNormalWorkers","goldSpeedWorkers","goldSpeedWarriors"
| json field=json_text "lastKnownSnailPosition"
| json field=json_text "secondsSinceGameStart"
| long(gameid) as gameid
| withtime blueBerriesRemaining | most_recent(blueBerriesRemaining_withtime) as blueBerriesRemaining
| fields blueBerriesRemaining
| concat(blueBerriesRemaining,"/12") as output
| fields output

panels.name: Game Clock
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$killerQueen gamestate
| parse "com.sumologic.killerqueen.state.StateMachine - *" as json_text | json field=json_text "event"
| json field=json_text "gameId"
| json field=json_text "lastKnownSnailPosition"
| json field=json_text "secondsSinceGameStart"
| int(secondsSinceGameStart) as secondsSinceGameStart
| long(gameid) as gameid
| max(secondsSinceGameStart) as secondsSinceGameStart by gameid 
| filter gameid in (max(gameid) as gameid)
| format("%.0f s", secondsSinceGameStart) as output
| fields output

panels.name: Military Win Status
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$killerQueen gamestate
| parse "com.sumologic.killerqueen.state.StateMachine - *" as json_text | json field=json_text "event"
| json field=json_text "gameId"
| json field=json_text "goldQueenLivesRemaining", "blueQueenLivesRemaining"
| json field=json_text "goldBerriesRemaining","blueBerriesRemaining"
| withtime blueQueenLivesRemaining
| withtime goldQueenLivesRemaining
| most_recent(blueQueenLivesRemaining_withtime) as blueQueenLivesRemaining,  most_recent(goldQueenLivesRemaining_withtime) as goldQueenLivesRemaining
| fields blueQueenLivesRemaining, goldQueenLivesRemaining
| "No \uD83E\uDD3A Leader" as output
| if( blueQueenLivesRemaining < goldQueenLivesRemaining, "Gold \uD83E\uDD3A leading", output) as output
| if( goldQueenLivesRemaining < blueQueenLivesRemaining, "Blue \uD83E\uDD3A leading", output) as output
| fields output

panels.name: Queen Lives Remaining
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$killerQueen gamestate
| parse "com.sumologic.killerqueen.state.StateMachine - *" as json_text | json field=json_text "event"
| json field=json_text "gameId"
| json field=json_text "goldQueenLivesRemaining", "blueQueenLivesRemaining"
| json field=json_text "goldBerriesRemaining","blueBerriesRemaining"
| withtime goldQueenLivesRemaining | most_recent(goldQueenLivesRemaining_withtime) as goldQueenLivesRemaining

| if(goldQueenLivesRemaining="3","\u2764\uFE0F\u2764\uFE0F\u2764\uFE0F",
  if(goldQueenLivesRemaining="2","\uD83D\uDC94\u2764\uFE0F\u2764\uFE0F","\uD83D\uDC94\uD83D\uDC94\u2764\uFE0F")) as output
//| concat(goldQueenLivesRemaining,"/3") as output
| fields output

panels.name: Harvesting Win Status
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$killerQueen gamestate
| parse "com.sumologic.killerqueen.state.StateMachine - *" as json_text | json field=json_text "event"
| json field=json_text "gameId"
| json field=json_text "goldQueenLivesRemaining", "blueQueenLivesRemaining"

| json field=json_text "lastKnownSnailPosition"
| json field=json_text "secondsSinceGameStart"
| long(gameid) as gameid

| withtime goldBerriesRemaining

panels.name: Snail Position
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$killerQueen gamestate
| parse "com.sumologic.killerqueen.state.StateMachine - *" as json_text | json field=json_text "event"
| json field=json_text "gameId"
| json field=json_text "lastKnownSnailPosition"
| json field=json_text "secondsSinceGameStart"
| int(secondsSinceGameStart) as secondsSinceGameStart
| long(gameid) as gameid
| int(secondsSinceGameStart) as secondsSinceGameStart
| max(lastKnownSnailPosition) as lastKnownSnailPosition by gameid, secondsSinceGameStart
| lastKnownSnailPosition - 960 as lastKnownSnailPosition
| sort secondsSinceGameStart asc
| filter gameid in (max(gameid) as gameid)
| -960 as blue
| 960 as gold
| fields secondsSinceGameStart, gold, blue, lastKnownSnailPosition

panels.name: Snail Win Status
panels.queryString:
_sourceCategory=$$killerQueen gamestate
| parse "com.sumologic.killerqueen.state.StateMachine - *" as json_text | json field=json_text "event"
| json field=json_text "gameId"
| json field=json_text "lastKnownSnailPosition"
| json field=json_text "secondsSinceGameStart"
| int(secondsSinceGameStart) as secondsSinceGameStart
| long(gameid) as gameid
| long(gameid) as gameid
| withtime lastKnownSnailPosition | most_recent(lastKnownSnailPosition_withtime) as lastKnownSnailPosition
| lastKnownSnailPosition - 1000 as lastKnownSnailPosition
| -960 as blue
| 960 as gold
| "No \uD83D\uDC0C Leader" as output
| if( lastKnownSnailPosition < -40, "Blue \uD83D\uDC0C leading", 
  if( lastKnownSnailPosition > -40, "Gold \uD83D\uDC0C leading","The \uD83D\uDC0C is contested")) as output
| fields output
